<br>
I'm a reclaim chainer, but I also use pet canni for my mana needs, particularly after a rez, or after heavy burning.<br>
<br>
After a rez, I'm usually FM and gtg before the rez effects wear off.  After a heavy burn, I only need to canni for 30-45 seconds to get back most of my mana.<br>
<br>
I don't understand your problem.<br>
