lor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=jochangaladar>Jochan Galadar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 919<br> <font color=#333333>(2/9/03 8:35:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=474.topic&index=46>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: dunno</span><hr size=1> You are making some odd assumptions.  The first assumption you are making is that most magicians sooner or later will get Gloves of Dark Summoning, an exceedingly rare drop in Vex Thall.  The second assumtion you are making is that most magicians sooner or later will also get Call of the Archmage, which requires a Glyphed Rune for the trade in quest.  The third assumtion you are making is that given a choice, most magicians would prefer to solo in Bastion of Thunder.  The fourth assumption is that 120 mana per reclaim is inadequate for personal mana regeneration, solo or grouped.  The fifth assumption you are making is that most magicians will prefer to solo at all.<br>
<br>
Reclaim chaining can be done in practically any zone.  I highly doubt you can say the same for our charm spell.  Improved Reclaim gives you a very nice balance for mana regeneration and mana free pets.  You can still charm with or without the skill, you will still have amazing mana regen, and if you need to you can chain pets forever if need be without worrying about your mana bar.<br>
<br>
By the way, 200+ mana regen is very nice indeed, but for at least some of us, that rate cannot be attained, with or without Improved Reclaim.  I will make the best of what I have access to. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=balanzsonofanz>Balanz son of Anz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Abuser of EZCodes</span><br>  Posts: 2873<br> <font color=#333333>(2/9/03 4:56:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=474.topic&index=47>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: dunno</span><hr size=1> There is nothing like a group of <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>IRE</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> mages chaining pets into a mob at no mana cost.<br>
